# Embed Guide — Next.js App Router

Generated by `/atw.embed` on {{generatedAt}}.

Answers captured in [`.atw/state/embed-answers.md`](../state/embed-answers.md).
The values below were **inlined from `.atw/config/project.md`** — you should
